Rating: 4
We have tuna salad sandwiches for lunch frequently and I've been working my way through various recipes. This one is a WINNER. My recommendations: use 2 hard-boiled eggs; increase green pepper to 3 tablespoons; increase scallions to 4 or 5 but use only white-to-light-green portion. I added 1 tablespoon minced fresh cilantro and WOWEE did that go over big at my house!

